[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "……ってことがあってね。\n光星隊は本格始動前に壊滅しちゃったの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00146",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私はヘルトとゼロに必ずやり返す……\n私を信じてついてきてくれた部下たちのためにも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00147",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ヘルトとゼロを追ってる理由は分かりましたけど……\nぶっちゃけ、勝てるんすか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00148",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "……うん？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00149",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ほら、なんかこう、必勝の策とか、\n伝説の武器を手に入れた、とか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00150",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "もちろん、いくつか作戦は立てたけどね、\nそこまで確かなものは、ないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00151",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そ、それじゃ見つけて戦っても\n同じように負けちゃうんじゃ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00152",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "それでもだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00153",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "光星隊を倒すほどの脅威を、私は王女としても\n光星隊隊長としても野放しにはできない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00154",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "赤子の手をひねるように壊滅させられて……あれでは\nランターナ王国が舐められているのと同じだもの！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00155",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "お、おお～……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00156",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（この人、レスナ側の人だ。何があっても諦めない\n　英雄側の人間……でも……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00157",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "次は、ないかもしれませんよ？　あいつらは……\nヘルトとゼロは命を奪うことも躊躇わない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00158",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あなた……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00159",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "どうして、あなたはそこまでできるんですか？\n誇りとか想いって、命より大事なんですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00160",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "死んだら、失敗したら……それで終わりなんですよ？\n復讐だって果たせないし、無駄死にじゃないですか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00161",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "その忠告、私のためを思って……じゃなくて、\n私に別の誰かさんを重ねているみたいだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00162",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あっ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00163",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "他人の気持ちを汲み取るのは得意なんだ。\n王族に求められる能力の１つだからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00164",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "で、これはあなたの求めている答えかどうかは\n分からないけれど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00165",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "危険は百も承知。私だって死にたくはない。\nでも、死ぬのを怖がってたら、一生進めない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00166",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "いつか勝ってみせる、じゃダメなんだって分かった。\nだって、その「いつか」はいつ来るの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00167",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "絶対勝てるようになるまで強くなってから挑むの？\n何年かかるの？　それまで立ち止まってるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00168",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "それは生きてない。ただ死んでないだけ……\n一生挑戦しないなら、いつまで経っても負け犬だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00169",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "一生挑戦しないなら、負け犬……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00170",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "馬鹿だ、無謀だなんてのは、軍に入った時に散々\n言われた。お姫様は城で大人しくしとけって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00171",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "でもね、私はなりたかったの。あらゆる意味でみんなを\n守れて、面倒を見られる王族にね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00172",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "もちろん、私の命は自分だけのものじゃない。\n民のみんなが支えてくれているもの……でも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00173",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ここで動かなきゃ、クレオ・ランターナじゃない。\n私の信じた、私じゃないの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00174",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そう、ですか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00175",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00176",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "お気持ちは承知いたしました。\nただ今からでは、雷鳴の島での決闘に間に合わない……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00177",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "下手に船で向かっても行き違いになってしまいます。\nここはレスナさんが彼らを連れ帰るのを待ちましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00178",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そうだね。物理的に間に合わないのは\nしょうがないもんね……分かった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00179",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "続報が入るまで、カフェで大人しくお客になるよ。\n腹が減っては戦ができぬ、だもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00180",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "え、ええ……ともかく、今はここで待っていたほうが。\nでは、アタシは、これで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00181",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "ごめんなさい、早退するから引き継ぎ頼めるかしら。\n後で絶対埋め合わせするから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00182",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]